<plot>After 10 years of performing together, music group COLORS calls it quits with a farewell concert captured with 6 cameras. This memorable DVD allows you to bring their music into your living room...forever. Along with their final concert the DVD includes other special features: Original Documentary COLORS: Upclose &amp; Personal, 10 Years of COLORS History, Bios &amp; Behind the Scenes footage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?111092</url></doc>
